      <a href="/products/#escalators" class="image-card"><img src="/assets/images/company/escalators.jpg" alt="Escalators in a commercial interior" loading="lazy"><span><strong>Escalators</strong><small>Continuous movement for busy public spaces</small></span></a>
      <a href="/products/#walkways" class="image-card"><img src="/assets/images/company/moving-walkway.jpg" alt="Moving walkway in an enclosed passage" loading="lazy"><span><strong>Moving Walkways</strong><small>Convenient horizontal and inclined movement</small></span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-padding" aria-labelledby="experience-title">
  <div class="container split-feature">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Established experience</p>
      <h2 id="experience-title">Serving complex buildings since 2006</h2>
      <p>Everest World Lifts was originally incorporated as Everest Elevators Ltd in June 2006 and adopted its current name in February 2019.</p>
      <p>Our corporate profile records elevator, escalator, installation, replacement, and maintenance work for government institutions, commercial facilities, hospitality businesses, and residential properties.</p>
      <a href="/projects/" class="btn btn-primary">View selected experience</a>
